 2024-13002024-12-09PS, TC
ActPreclearance Act, 2016
SubjectRegulations Amending the Preclearance in Canada Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the PRECLEARANCE IN CANADA REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) clarify that transfer of seized or detained goods from a U.S. preclearance officer be made to a person with relevant Canadian authority to receive it; and (2) correct a discrepancy between English and French versions.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2024-0261 Publication Date: 2024-12-18
AttachmentsAttachment
